### Test Expense Limit API

### 1. Set Monthly Limit for Category (Current Month)
POST https://localhost:7062/api/ExpenseLimit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "categoryId": 1,
  "amount": 500.00
}

### 2. Set Monthly Limit for Specific Month
POST https://localhost:7062/api/ExpenseLimit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "categoryId": 2,
  "amount": 300.00,
  "month": 1,
  "year": 2026
}

### 3. Get Limit Status for Category (Current Month)
GET https://localhost:7062/api/ExpenseLimit/1/category/1

### 4. Get Limit Status for Specific Month
GET https://localhost:7062/api/ExpenseLimit/1/category/2?month=1&year=2026

### 5. Get All Limits for User (Current Month)
GET https://localhost:7062/api/ExpenseLimit/1

### 6. Get All Limits for Specific Month
GET https://localhost:7062/api/ExpenseLimit/1?month=1&year=2026

### 7. Delete Limit
DELETE https://localhost:7062/api/ExpenseLimit/1/category/1

### 8. Delete Limit for Specific Month
DELETE https://localhost:7062/api/ExpenseLimit/1/category/2?month=1&year=2026
